internal.content: To make it easy for everyone to test the leading edge of axe-core, we’ve introduced this new free Chrome extension, called axe Coconut. It includes our latest code changes for Shadow DOM, with experimental rules also enabled.

internal.content: The first step to ensure an acessible website is to have enough color contrast in your colors so that everyone can read and the contrast ratio in the chrome dev tools color picker is a huge help.
